name: TheGoetia [Helluva Boss] NSFW [Fluffusion]
description:
After days of pain and paying for google colab, I bring forth, v4(.20)

A Helluva Boss themed LoRa.

V4. Features: (ALMOST) ALL THE CAST!

TheGoetia aims to be an all-in-one LoRa for Helluva Boss characters. Works best with Fluffusion e20 and any other model based on e621 tagging or training (like FluffyRock).

NSFW enabled.

Trigger words are now self-explained and listed bellow due to the amount of custom tags.

Known issues:

  • stolas' clothes turned into a mess I am sorry but it's a sacrifice I had to make (worked on later epoch but the characters were overcooked by then).

  • Unpopular characters work the least, since there is close to no images and all data had to be taken from the show directly.

  • This version requires the most impaint to be done I feel like, so either that or regional prompting.

    Group rendering requires additional context tags. You know which I am talking about. Also for the baby tags, those require certain words that are unique to the genre of baby characters.

Known issues:

  • octaviabottom and octaviasweater work 5% of the time, artists seems to influence this success rate.
